S.FORM: Joe Alexander unu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u misimaw zikuzay mimaliay, u adidi'ay ayaway mimaliay, tabakiay ayaway mimaliay, tebanay mimaliay.
